<SUMMARY>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=2 -->
SUMMARY:
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
 The Commodity Credit Corporation (CCC) is issuing this final rule which revises the regulations for the Export Credit
Guarantee Program (GSM&hyph;102) and the Intermediate Export Credit Guarantee Program (GSM&hyph;103). In addition
to making changes intended to improve and update the current regulations, this final rule also incorporates material
required by the Agricultural Trade Act of 1978, as amended by Section 1531 of the Food, Agriculture, Conservation,
and Trade Act of 1990 (the 1990 Act). 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 02 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
</SUMMARY>
<DATE>
<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=2 -->
EFFECTIVE DATE:
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
 The provisions of this final rule are effective November 18, 1994.
