<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
1493.5&blank;Criteria for agricultural commodity allocations. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
1493.6&blank;Additional required determinations for GSM&hyph;103.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 02 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=72 g=1 f=1 -->
Subpart B_CCC Export Credit Guarantee Program (GSM&hyph;102) and CCC Intermediate Export Credit Guarantee Program
(GSM&hyph;103) Operations
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=20 g=1 f=1 -->
Sec. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=26 g=1 f=1 -->
1493.10&blank;General statement.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
1493.20&blank;Definition of terms.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
1493.30&blank;Information required for program participation.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
1493.40&blank;Application for a payment guarantee.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
1493.50&blank;Certification requirements for obtaining payment guarantee.
